@node About "Author information and credits"

@{b}@{u}About ARexx.guide@{uu}@{ub}

This  AmigaGuide  document  was  created by Troels Walsted Hansen with
layout  inspiration taken from termRexx.guide by Olaf Barthel and some
text  taken  from  Petter Nilsen's example scripts.  Modified for THOR
2.0  by Petter Nilsen.  Some text was also taken from Marius' original
documentation for the FSE (the internal editor in THOR).  Eirik Synnes
updated the guide for the Thor 2.6 release.

